rows.label: qst702004_msg0001
rows.name:
Could these be Kai-kun and Kei-chan's
footprints...?

rows.label: qst702004_msg0101
rows.name: Two sets of prints. We should follow.

rows.label: qst702004_msg0301
rows.name: There we go, Kai and Kei's trail...

rows.label: qst702004_msg0401
rows.name: Let's use the footprints to track them.

rows.label: qst702004_msg0501
rows.name: Footprints. We can track 'em this way.

rows.label: qst702004_msg0601
rows.name:
We ought to follow Kai and Kei's
footprints.

rows.label: qst702004_msg0701
rows.name: Where could they have run off to...?

rows.label: qst702004_msg0801
rows.name: I pray the children are unharmed...
